Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This girl is Kouyama Mitsuki. 12 years old!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.38,0:00:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's become the singer{\i1} Full Moon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and has had her first taste of work, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:06.52,0:00:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she keeps worrying about whether or not she seems enough like an adult.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.19,0:00:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In the end, she was even scolded!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, after talking with the local female high school students...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.45,0:00:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she realized that it was fine to accept the futility in trying to become an adult, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she managed to complete her job safely.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.28,0:00:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.09,0:00:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.91,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.65,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,460)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.20,0:00:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,460)}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:36.05,0:00:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.30,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wanna go too!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.48,0:00:44.39,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can't.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:44.39,0:00:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You have to turn into Mitsuki and watch the house.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.96,0:00:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you don't do that, her grandmother will realize that she went out.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.64,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.32,0:00:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I haven't had to do this before, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no way we can use visiting \NWakaouji-sensei as an excuse today...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.99,0:01:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...which means that someone has to take her place.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.20,0:01:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We can't do anything if I'm not there to change her into a sixteen year old.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.59,0:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That leaves you.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no one else who can do it.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.72,0:01:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Today's a very important recording session for my debut.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So... okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:20.43,0:01:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But you know...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Every once in a while, you have to watch the house, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.69,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.69,0:01:26.06,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!{layer made 2}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:23.93,0:01:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\be1}I want to go out too you know...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.23,0:01:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.23,0:01:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Selfish pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:36.74,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Sign,{\pos(330,340)\bord2.5}The Long Day in the Studio
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that the studio?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's a whole bunch of fans!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.59,0:01:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.34,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...who is it that's coming, I wonder...?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It doesn't matter who it is, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}More importantly...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh! Who is it?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.98,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who is it?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.35,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! Wait up!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's the Guitar Boys!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're going to record now?!{}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Amazing!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Didn't you come here to record, too?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.20,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.24,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... {\alphaFF}But...{alpha timed because of contiguous but... s}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.99,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... But...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man... Let's go.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well then, I'll get on here.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey! Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Ooshige-san!{}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over here!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.22,0:03:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hurry up and come here!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't like this... everyone's looking at me.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're a singer... that's how it's going to be. \NNothing you can really do about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah... {Where the heck did a.f.k get "I guess so" from anyway}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A talking stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well? {How are you? replaced because the timing is too short to read it.}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did you get enough sleep last night?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah. For now...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.67,0:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then we're okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's work hard today!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.11,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on, go in.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I feel... somewhat overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... excuse me.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have a job to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She'll be recording here starting today...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.46,0:04:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. I'm Full Moon.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a pleasure to be working with you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Be strong. Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.67,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It hurts...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Sorry, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm watching over you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ow. Ow. Ow. Ow. Ow.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is she going to be okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please come over here.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... promise me.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You'll definitely stay here and watch me.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.71,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.10,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm caught.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What? It's just you guys.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You came again?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If they find you, we don't know you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Putting that aside...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did you see a girl carrying a stuffed animal cat?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A cat?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.02,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The one who just went in that studio.
