Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's somewhat... peaceful in here.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So that unnecessary noise won't be picked up...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.93,0:05:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we went all out in building this room.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that so?
