Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... please wait a bit.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Ah. Ahem. Ahem. Ahem.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Ah. Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to sing in here...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.95,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.12,0:05:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse us...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We need to run a mic check, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...can you say something?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.37,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Uwa...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.17,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Uwa...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.38,0:06:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. We can hear you.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Producer Takasu. {producer is an honorific now, what has the world come to}{Maybe it can change it to Producer Takasu?}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.86,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yo.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.85,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You feeling up to this?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes. Somehow...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For now... here's {\i1}Myself{\i0}... {Myself, but erm, misedit in the original script}{edited back to Myself}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Try singing it. {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.34,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... music please.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.48,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... start by putting your headphones on.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Headphones?{Head-hon?}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You put on your headphones so that you can hear the music.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Is that what it is?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Technology has sure come a long way.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's a fun girl, isn't she?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As an amateur, this is her first time in all of this.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Since she's new at this...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we'll take it slowly.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is going to take up so much time.
