Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:58.27,Myself TL(Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,,{\be2}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:04.40,Myself Romaji (Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,,{\be2\k28}Ki{\k20}mi {\k35}no {\k25}ko{\k48}e {\k21}ka{\k11}na{\k23}shi{\k23}i {\k24}ho{\k55}do {\k17}hi{\k93}bi{\k41}te{\k20}ru {\k108}yo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:04.40,Myself TL(Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,,{\be2}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.73,Myself Romaji (Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,,{\be2\k42}I{\k68}ma {\kf0}ma-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.73,Myself TL(Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,,{\be2}I never...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.57,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,435)}Ah, wait a second.{}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're bringing out the loneliness at this part, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it would be better if you showed the feeling of serenity with which you wrote them.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Serenity?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't have to sing well... just put your feelings.{put}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So then... let's try it.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.39,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kitty-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A date, right now?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wah! I'll go! I'll go!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where are you going to take me?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You really like me that much, huh.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I also like you, of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why can't that ever happen every once in a while?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I should...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.82,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Now I can't go outside and play.{she is thinking here while waving and responding to Tanaka-san}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You still look a little nervous.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We've been looking at it for a while here, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How about a break?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:24.98,0:08:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki. Is your throat dry?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.93,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you want some coffee?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you know what happened to the stuffed animal cat that was here?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.82,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The members of Guitar Boys! {last line was too awkward}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... actually...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.59,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you a new girl?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're {\i1}Full Moon,{\i0} aren't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.80,0:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How old are you?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.86,0:08:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...looking for a stuffed animal cat...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you know anything about one?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.06,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A stuffed animal cat?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.27,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Dunno...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, now that you mention it... just a moment ago...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I saw Nanami-chan carrying something like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where did that girl go?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where...?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She went home already, didn't she?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you know where she lives at? {}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have no clue... about something like that...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.26,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.41,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.16,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! Kitty-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're awake?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:32.47,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wha..?{}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Won't you talk with me?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on!!!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.56,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ow. Ow. Ow. Ow. Ow.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stupid! That hurts!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He talked!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man... spare me already.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.15,0:09:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}See ya.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.95,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kitty-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where are you? Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kitty-chan disappeared.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't do this to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yay!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kitty-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't go back to her at this rate.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.14,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Whee!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez... Takuto, where are you?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.12,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When I'm not with you...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.09,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...use this whistle to call me.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.31,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll fly to you.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.93,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There isn't any sound coming out...?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm? She's calling for me.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.52,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't just talk to yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Talk to me!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmph.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Say something!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.74,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Owwwww!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! You talked!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're {\i1}that{\i0}  happy when I talk?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm happy!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm not happy, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'm leaving, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry, but I'm busy.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why not?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kitty-chan is...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...my friend!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't decide that I'm your friend on your own!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you're going to say that...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...then I'll do this!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.18,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\be1}Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.18,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I get it! I get it, so stop!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's play together, then.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.56,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're even worse than Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! I'm bored.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.62,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Those two haven't come back yet. {No Takuto-tachi here, damnit}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.78,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscy90\fscx90}When in the kitchen, dealing with oil is always a problem.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscy90\fscx90}That's right!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8\fscy90\fscx90}Until now...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.00,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For heaven's sake...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.93,0:12:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who left the television on?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hold it...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You won't even let me watch television?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By the way, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you know what Mitsuki is doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes. I'll go get her right away.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.98,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm not joking!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she's had to put up with this kind of life?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At this rate...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I don't find Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This whistle is definitely broken! {Translation: This whistle sucks!}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can hear it.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yo.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just... what?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on, Kitty-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't wander off on your own! {a.f.k untranslated it, so best guesslation}{replaced thanks to convexity}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.10,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Will you give me back that stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.59,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nope!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because it's mine!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.71,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it's really mine.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No it's not!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's mine!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't understand it either.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.11,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kitty-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your name is Takuto?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.49,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:27.41,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're my friend, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You took me away while I was \Nsleeping without even asking...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...friends don't do things like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}While you were asleep?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:37.49,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're mean, Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You said that you'd listen to me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A-A-At that time, you were still practicing.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was totally awake while you were recording.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.13,0:13:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What about your recording?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.89,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just now...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...they called to say they weren't ready yet, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.60,0:13:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't talk to my Takuto so familiarly.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know... Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto belongs to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Show me proof then.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't have any proof, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...but he's mine.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're the singer{\i1} Full Moon,{\i0} right?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.32,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You should hurry up and go back to the studio, shouldn't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you don't give me back Takuto, I can't sing!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's such a childish thing to say.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's because...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back home.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's it!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This place is my home.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.97,0:14:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.85,0:14:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go in, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, what do you want to play?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Will it be okay if you don't go home?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.44,0:14:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your father and your mother will be worried.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They won't be.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.78,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because I don't have any.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.79,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.82,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't have a father or mother?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.41,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're... all alone?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.12,0:14:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, here we go!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yay!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is fun!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go again!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.32,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.12,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun lost his...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.16,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Me, too...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here we go!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yay!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you having fun, Nanami-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep. I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami-chan, you're lonely, aren't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm not lonely at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's a lie. {Mitsuki's character accusing of someone as a lier? edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because you're lonely...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you took Takuto, didn't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... if I say I'm lonely...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...is it okay if I don't give Takuto back?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.91,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is it okay for me to be with Takuto forever?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.71,0:16:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As if.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everything I said was a lie.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My father and mother are over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hold it!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.28,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.47,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}See.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's my father and mother.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's a lie too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It is?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.74,0:16:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:52.69,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your total comes to 933 yen.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.16,0:16:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.38,0:16:57.83,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A thousand yen, is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder what should I get.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you have a mother...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...then why won't she make dinner for you?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's because she's busy.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are they really your father and mother?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.45,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll get this.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.09,0:17:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's true.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When you entered the store...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...they didn't say anything to you at all, did they?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's how it always is.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Always...?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Every day.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.06,0:17:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You mean that you eat dinner by yourself every day?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Every day?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is too strange.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If they're your real father and mother...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...why don't they say anything?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If they were your real family...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When you go home...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.88,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you'd say "I'm home", and they'd say "welcome back", right?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because I...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I had a father and mother...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I would say "I'm home", and I would want them to say "welcome back" to me!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.90,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And you say that you have parents...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.77,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because I also want...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...to talk to my father and mother, and...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...there are lots of things I want to talk about.{}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're always busy, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.72,0:18:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mama!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mama! Mama!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry, Nanami.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.03,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We couldn't...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...take proper care of you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're so sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please forgive us.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.63,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nanami...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Papa!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't this great, Nanami-chan? {Since a.f.k ommited an honorific in this line, they should have just localized this whole show}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Onee-chan, here.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm very sorry for taking Takuto without asking.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.43,0:19:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My, my.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was wondering about what would happen.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey. Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you want to go to the recording with me?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.03,0:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.74,0:19:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This time...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You won't have to do it secretly.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.07,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's good, isn't she?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's giving off an aura of serenity.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By the way, who is she?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Full Moon's Number One Fan.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on, it's okay, isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Costume, check!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Makeup, check!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, Takuto!
